# start Validation Reply Form
_vrf_THETM01_P21n_a
;
PROBLEM: The value of sine(theta_max)/wavelength is less than 0.575
RESPONSE: Due to the heavy disorder of the highly symmetric, perfluorinated 
aluminumalkoxide anions the scattering power and ultimately the theta_max 
values are very little.
;
_vrf_PLAT019_P21n_a
;
PROBLEM: _diffrn_measured_fraction_theta_full/_max < 1.0      0.773 Report
RESPONSE: This alert is also a result of the weak scattering power of the
highly disordered aluminumalkoxide anions (see above).
;
# end Validation Reply Form
 
